TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: Nghin cu cc phng php h tr nh v chnh xc
Tc gi lun vn: Hong Trung Tuyn Kho: 2012B
Ngi hng dn: TS. H Duyn Trung
NI DUNG TM TT
1. L do chn ti
nh v v dn ng tr nn v cng cp thit, khng th thiu trong cc
lnh vc ca i sng x hi, an ninh quc phng... Tuy nhin h thng khng th t
c s chnh xc tuyt i. V vy cn phi tng chnh xc ca h thng nh v
ton cu. Bng cch khc phc c sai s ca h thng dn ng (GPS) v h thng
dn ng qun tnh (INS) .
H thng dn ng qun tnh INS c hai u im ni bt khi so snh vi cc h
thng dn ng khc l kh nng hot ng t tr v chnh xc cao trong nhng
khong thi gian ngn. Li nghim trng nht ca h thng INS l do cc cm bin
qun tnh gy ra. Chnh v th trong nhng ng dng thi gian di th h thng INS
thng s dng vi cc h thng h tr khc nh h thng dn ng v tuyn. S kt
hp GPS v INS l l tng nht v hai h thng ny c kh nng b tr nhau hiu
qu. Tri tim ca h thng tch hp ny chnh l b lc ti u Kalman.
2. Mc ch, i tng, phm vi, phng php nghin cu
2.1. Mc ch nghin cu
Nghin cu v h thng dn ng nh v GPS tch hp vi h thng dn
ng qun tnh INS (Inertial Navigation System).
2.2. i tng nghin cu
- Nghin cu l thuyt v h thng nh v ton cu GPS;
- Nghin cu l thuyt h thng dn ng qun tnh INS;
- Nghin cu l thuyt v m phng b lc Kalman trong h thng GPS/INS s
dng phn mm Matlab.
2.3. Phm vi nghin cu
Nghin cu cc vn l thuyt v m phng h thng GPS/INS.
2
2.4. Phng php nghin cu
- Phng php nghin cu l thuyt
- Phng php xin kin chuyn gia
3. Ni dung chnh ca lun vn v ng gp ca tc gi
Chng 1: Tng quan v thng nh v ton cu GPS. Gii thiu khi qut v
h thng nh v ton cu GPS bao gm cc khi nim, thnh phn v nguyn l hot
ng ca h thng.
Chng 2: Cc ngun gy sai s v mt s phng php h tr nh v chnh
xc. Trnh by cc ngun (nguyn nhn) gy sai s trong h thng nh v ton cu
GPS, nh gi v a ra mt s phng php h tr nh v chnh xc.
Chng 3: H thng nh v v dn ng qun tnh GPS/INS. Gii thiu v
h thng dn ng qun tnh INS, cc khi nim c bn, cu trc h thng, xy dng
b lc Kalman v kt qu m phng trn Matlab khi kt hp GPS/INS.
4. Kt lun
Hin nay, h thng nh v ton cu GPS c ng dng ph bin trn th
gii nhng mt xu hng mi xut hin l kt hp GPS vi h dn ng qun tnh
INS nhm tn dng trit u im v gim thiu sai s ca c hai phng php ny.
Lun vn i su phn tch, nh gi v m phng h thng INS, v vy t c
mt s kt qu sau:
- Tm hiu c cu trc, thnh phn, hot ng v ng dng ca h thng
GPS. Nhng ngun sai s trong h nh v GPS mt v mt s bin php khc phc.
- Tm hiu c tng quan h thng dn ng qun tnh INS. Tm hiu cu
trc lc ti u Kalman v xy dng b lc Kalman ci tin cho h dn ng qun
tnh INS trong Matlab.
chnh xc ca h thng tch hp GPS/INS cao hn c chnh xc ca h
thng GPS hay INS khi hot ng c lp. chnh xc ny s c nng cao nu
tng s trng thi ca b lc Kalman v m hnh ho c cc tc nhn gy li khc
na ca cm bin qun tnh. R rng l xu hng kt hp GPS/INS l xu hng tt
yu ca vn nh v v dn ng trong tng lai.
